nodes.text: The Elders of the Oswaft were the leaders of the vacuum-breathing species dwelling in the ThonBoka. Due to their age and wisdom, they were called upon to make the decisions concerning the entire population. The meeting place for the council was the Cave of Elders, located in the center of the ThonBoka Nebula.
In 3 BBY, they numbered three, with the chief Elder being Senwannus'gourkahipaff, and his second was Feytihennasraof. Bhoggihalysahonues was the third and youngest of the group.
